#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn52.24:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. A Thousand "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 24. Āsavakkhayasutta → vijjā 3 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn52.24:0.3"
msgid "24. Āsavakkhayasutta "
msgstr "24. The Ending of Defilements "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.306, sc1
msgctxt "sn52.24:1.1"
msgid "“Imesañca panāhaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharāmī”ti. "
msgstr "“… And it’s because of developing and cultivating these four kinds of mindfulness meditation that I realized the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life. And I live having realized it with my own insight due to the ending of defilements.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn52.24:1.2"
msgid "Cuddasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn52.24:1.3"
msgid "Dutiyo vaggo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn52.24:2.1"
msgid "Mahābhiññaṃ iddhi dibbaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn52.24:2.2"
msgid "Cetopariyaṃ ṭhānaṃ kammaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn52.24:2.3"
msgid "Sabbatthadhātudhimutti, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn52.24:2.4"
msgid "Indriyaṃ jhānaṃ tisso vijjāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn52.24:2.5"
msgid "Anuruddhasaṃyuttaṃ aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr "The Linked Discourses with Anuruddha are the eighth section."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
